data.title: Oklahoma City Thunder Roster
data.meta_description: Oklahoma City Thunder scores, news, schedule, players, stats, rumors, depth charts and more on RealGM.com
data.text:
Josh Giddey was selected as the #6 pick in the First Round of the 2021 NBA Draft by the Oklahoma City Thunder. Josh Giddey signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on August 7, 2021.

Chet Holmgren was selected as the #2 pick in the First Round of the 2022 NBA Draft by the Oklahoma City Thunder. Chet Holmgren signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 1, 2022.

Jalen Williams was selected as the #12 pick in the First Round of the 2022 NBA Draft by the Oklahoma City Thunder. Jalen Williams signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 1, 2022.

Jaylin Williams was selected as the #4 pick in the Second Round of the 2022 NBA Draft by the Oklahoma City Thunder. Jaylin Williams signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 19, 2022.

Draft Rights to Ousmane Dieng, the #11 pick in the First Round of the 2022 NBA Draft, were acquired by the Oklahoma City Thunder from the New York Knicks on June 23, 2022. Ousmane Dieng signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 5, 2022.

Draft Rights to Cason Wallace, the #10 pick in the First Round of the 2023 NBA Draft, were acquired by the Oklahoma City Thunder from the Dallas Mavericks on July 6, 2023. Cason Wallace signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 7, 2023.

Shai Gilgeous-Alexander was acquired in a trade by the Oklahoma City Thunder from the Los Angeles Clippers on July 10, 2019. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander signed a multi-year extension with the Oklahoma City Thunder on August 6, 2021.

Gordon Hayward was acquired in a trade by the Oklahoma City Thunder from the Charlotte Hornets on February 8, 2024.

Bismack Biyombo signed a contract as a free agent with the Oklahoma City Thunder on February 10, 2024.

Luguentz Dort signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on June 24, 2020. Luguentz Dort re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 6, 2022.

Isaiah Joe signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Oklahoma City Thunder on October 16, 2022.

Mike Muscala signed a contract as a free agent with the Oklahoma City Thunder on March 2, 2024.

Lindy Waters III signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder on February 27, 2023. Lindy Waters III re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Oklahoma City Thunder on February 9, 2024.

Aaron Wiggins signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Oklahoma City Thunder on February 12, 2022.

Kenrich Williams signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 20, 2022.
